            <div corresp="#c6126f2">
                <head>Berlin, Germany</head>
                <p>H. Tildaberger, lately Consul at Geneva, detailed to Embassy at Berlin as a
                    Foreign Service officer; apptd. a Secy in Dipl. Service, June 22, 1936;</p>
                <p>P. Leverich, regularly V.C. at Berlin, detailed teuf. as 3d Secy of Embassy, July
                    19, 1937, assgd. Germany and as 3d Secy of Embassy, Aug. 14, 1937.</p>
                <p>Henry P. Leverick was designated 3d Secy. at Lisbon (D.A.'s memo # 516, dated
                    Feb. 18, 1941)</p>
            </div>
